{"tid":1059972,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[求大神] 想搵套睇過嘅動漫，但唔知係乜","createTime":"2019-03-13T12:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T13:22:15.000Z","uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f6c074e3fd60a2067a715334a2eb81dba2b0224","tid":1059972,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"之前喺youtube無啦啦碌到有條動漫片，大概幾分鐘，<br />\n條片入面係間屋，有個女人喺入面，仲有條屍，<br />\n條屍係咁爆血出嚟，條女就勁驚咁諗辦法幫條屍止血+清理，<br />\n間屋出面同時好似有個男人拍門想入嚟，類似擔心條女發生咩事，<br />\n條女一路止血但止極都止唔到，啲血仲要流得越嚟越勁，搞到條女就嚟崩潰咁痴晒線，<br />\n到最後出面條仔開咗門，之後就唔記得咗係點<br />\n<br />\n有無人知係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b81b2c3fb7d95c3c29b49a3751fee4af0e2817f","tid":1059972,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0565dd0418b063f029fd61908c560d3de81cbff9","tid":1059972,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3893ec2b3a672e398cfc7ad575858407d2d3e6e","tid":1059972,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af33755d47bf1ad9a700a03406c6f6e759a5a6e0","tid":1059972,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13